Note: Get blob properties
Process called "get_blob_properties" that takes blob_name as String and container_name as String and account_name as String returns AzureBlob:
    Let parameters be list containing
    Add "--name" to parameters
    Add blob_name to parameters
    Add "--container-name" to parameters
    Add container_name to parameters
